{"tid":594752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"達賴喇嘛：西藏可按「歐盟模式」處理","createTime":"2018-03-16T05:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T06:21:34.000Z","uid":35790,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b7d55bdd8d9508edf4baab04bd0e71b91dfb5c","tid":594752,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:42:19.000Z","msg":"達賴喇嘛：西藏可按「歐盟模式」處理<br />\n2018-03-16 13:17<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕在中國修憲取消國家正副主席任期制後，第十四世達賴喇嘛在「國際聲援西藏運動」成立30年大會上表示，支持西藏以「歐盟模式」留在中國內。<br />\n《路透》報導，第十四世達賴喇嘛昨（15）在「國際聲援西藏運動」成立30年大會上，以影片表示他「很欣賞歐盟精神」，並稱「共同利益比單獨國家的利益更重要。有了這樣的概念，我非常願意留在中華人民共和國境內」，也表示「中共國名中的『共和國』，代表了某種形式的聯合」。<br />\n中共當局則視達賴喇嘛為西藏分裂主義分子，並於上月要求德國賓士汽車，撤下其官方Instagram上引用達賴喇嘛名言的貼文。<br />\n&lt;自由時報&gt;"},{"pid":"cc039dae740cd2c41ef4d5c86833f72efede3278","tid":594752,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"中華聯邦？"},{"pid":"aee1b38ba2825a64b2903a2b37ec02bade0ee3fb","tid":594752,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"有人又可以打飛機"},{"pid":"0806676d72680c51e2808d9c95d3f4fd18d9b065","tid":594752,"uid":59898,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 然後脫歐"},{"pid":"b71b5665848a14c3a9d23f28a5ce2a79a2bf20b2","tid":594752,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"歐盟模式即係國與國關係"},{"pid":"50ea67813cb69edc4946bb72ffbc615041a7a583","tid":594752,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b71b5665848a14c3a9d23f28a5ce2a79a2bf20b2","tid":594752,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:10:04.000Z","msg":"歐盟模式即係國與國關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed2e294e0d29eadd05e81a98a9d8352138505eb","tid":594752,"uid":158270,"like":1,"d